data.description: Home sweet home! Large home for the growing family, well maintained, new HVAC, freshly painted, new toilets, gutter guards, kitchen with backsplash, new garbage disposal, new ceiling fans. Nice size bedrooms, 2 full size kitchens, new fridge in 2nd kitchen, wet bar on first floor, 2 wood burning fireplaces, cedar plank 4 season sunroom. So much to offer, this home is unique, it's like 2 separate homes. 2nd floor balcony with amazing sunrise and sunset views. A must see!  4 minutes to OSU Newark. Agent owned.
